      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe or maybe even higher. we're trying to get a really clear picture of our \"dream client\" for the global launch. can you help me profile the ideal consumer? i need a detailed breakdown of their lifestyle, what they value, and also their typical ethnic and cultural background so we can tailor the imagery and the vibe of the ads to hit home.",
